parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Slipping or Popping Out of Gear
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping or popping out of gear can cause loss of control, accidents, or leave the driver stranded, especially when driving on high-speed roads with close traffic behind.
symptoms: The transmission slips out of gear
especially in 4th gear
while accelerating under normal load; the transmission pops out of gear without warning; the vehicle goes into neutral without cause.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A cracked left side wheel hub can cause loss of control, accidents, or fatalities, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: Cracked left side wheel hub
which can lead to wheel failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A defective clutch basket mechanism can cause poor performance, vibration, and noise, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Clutch basket assembly is extremely sloppy in fit; vehicle exhibits extreme noise and vibration from the clutch area; clutch shudders and performs poorly.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Oil Leaks from Cylinder Base Gasket
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Oil leaks from the cylinder base gasket can cause the bike to crash if sufficient oil is deposited on the rear tire, leading to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: Oil leaking from the engine
oil dripping onto the rear tire
smoke coming from under the hood
oil leaking from the muffler air box.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive oil consumption can lead to engine seizure, resulting in accidents, injuries, and even death.
symptoms: High oil consumption
smoking from the engine
oil burning more than 1 quart in 600 miles.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Water Ingress into Spark Plug and Cylinder
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water ingress into the spark plug and cylinder can cause misfires or complete engine failure, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Water getting into the front spark plug
front cylinder misfiring or stopping firing
water shield construction fails to prevent water ingress.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A crack in the fuel tank can cause fuel leaks, which can lead to fires, explosions, or accidents, posing a significant safety risk to the rider and others on the road.
symptoms: Gas smell coming from the bike
crack in the fuel tank
fuel leaks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The faulty fuel injection system can cause surging, stalling, and uneven engine performance, making it difficult or impossible to operate the vehicle safely, which can lead to accidents or leave the rider stranded.
symptoms: Surging
stalling
backfiring
missing
and uneven engine performance
inability to maintain a constant RPM.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling without cause can cause loss of control, accidents, or leave the rider stranded, posing a safety risk to the rider and others on the road.
symptoms: Engine stalling without cause.
